#Method void drawLine(SkScalar x0, SkScalar y0, SkScalar x1, SkScalar y1, const SkPaint& paint)

Draw line segment from (x0, y0) to (x1, y1) using Canvas_Clip, Canvas_Matrix, and Paint paint.
In paint: Stroke_Width describes the line thickness; Stroke_Cap draws the end rounded or square;
Paint_Style is ignored, as if were set to SkPaint_kStroke_Style.

